extends .layout.pug
block header 
    h1 !{currentPage.titleHtml || currentPage.title || currentPage.name}
    p Learn more about the people behind the scenes.

block content
    section
        h2(data-title='Our team')
            | Lenra'
            |
            strong team
        section.tab.filter
            input#all(type="radio" name="tab" checked)
            label(for="all") All team
            input#head(type="radio" name="tab")
            label(for="head") Head
            input#developers(type="radio" name="tab")
            label(for="developers") Developers
            ul
                li.head.developers
                    img(src="../img/team/thomas.jpg" alt="Thomas Da Rocha")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Thomas Da Rocha
                            p CEO
                            nav.social
                                a.lenra-icon-github(href="https://github.com/taorepoara" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                                a.lenra-icon-linkedin(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-da-rocha-57211170" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Thomas Da Rocha is the CEO of the company.
                            | He is the head of the project.
                            | He works on both the frontend and backend and decides the direction to take for each progress made on the application.
                li.head
                    img(src="../img/team/alienor.jpg" alt="Aliénor Malbosc")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Aliénor Malbosc
                            p Community Manager
                            nav.social
                                a.lenra-icon-linkedin(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aliénor-malbosc-b03609220" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Aliénor Malbosc is the Community Manager, she takes care of the digital communication strategy, she manages our social networks.
                li.head
                    img(src="../img/team/nathalie.jpg" alt="Nathalie Pestel")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Nathalie Pestel
                            p CMO
                            nav.social 
                                a.lenra-icon-linkedin(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathalie-monrouzeau-822b9387" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Nathalie Pestel arrived just after Thomas Da Rocha.
                            | She is the CMO of the company, she takes care of the accounting as well.
                li.developers
                    img(src="../img/team/louis.jpg" alt="Louis Guilbert")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Louis Guilbert
                            p Full Stack Developer
                            nav.social 
                                a.lenra-icon-github(href="https://github.com/Nesqwik" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Louis Guilbert joined in March 2020.
                            | He is a full stack developer who does both frontend and backend and also has a global view on the project that gives him agility to intervene on any blocking problem.
                li.developers
                    img(src="../img/team/jonas.jpg" alt="Jonas Martinez")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Jonas Martinez
                            p Front-end Developer
                            nav.social 
                                a.lenra-icon-github(href="https://github.com/jonas-martinez" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Jonas Martinez is a former student of the company who is now in permanent employment and is in charge of the frontend and more precisely of the present and future functionalities of the application for the moment.
                            | He's an expert in Flutter and Dart technologies.
                li.developers
                    img(src="../img/team/emric.jpg" alt="Emric Pichonier")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Emric Pichonier
                            p Back-end Developer
                            nav.social 
                                a.lenra-icon-github(href="https://github.com/pichoemr" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Emric Pichonnier is a student at the end of his year at the university, he specializes in the backend part of IT and data management.
                li.developers
                    img(src="../img/team/flavien.jpg" alt="Flavien Cadet")
                    details  
                        summary
                            h3 Flavien Cadet
                            p DevSecOps
                            nav.social
                                a.lenra-icon-github(href="https://github.com/shiipou" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                        p
                            | Flavien Cadet joined the company in 2018 as a work-study student while he was finishing his Master 1 and Master 2.
                            | Then he became an employee in early 2020.
                            | He is mainly in charge of the backend part but has a lot of knowledge that allows him to visualize the whole project and help Thomas Da Rocha to make decisions as best as he can.
                            | He is the SecOp Dev on the project.

    section#len.alternate
        h2(data-title='Discover our rubber duck debugger')
            | Meet
            |
            strong Len Racoon
        p
            | Len Racoon, our 'rubber duck' debugger.
            | He was born in november 2021, from Thomas' creative mind.
            | The super Budsies company made him come true.
            | He now helps us daily to debug code, understand and solve problems, as his cute and peaceful face tells us 'be confident, explain it all to me, you're gonna find an answer'....
        img(src="img/team/len.jpg" alt="Len Racoon" loading="lazy")

